{
  "texts": [
    "All patient-related metadata was eliminated.",
    "A professional clinician chooses video segments with polyps.",
    "Then resized the video frames to 560 × 480 after removing the black borders and sampled 160 videos with 40,266 frames each with 200 polyps, ensuring that each video had at least one polyp.",
    "There are a total of 33,884 frames with at least one polyp.",
    "The LDPolypVideo dataset (Fig. 22) sets a new standard for computer-aided polyp identification and diagnostic research."
  ]
}